<div class="section section-accordion shop-shipping" id="shopShipping">
	<div class="section-header">
		<h3 class="title">3. Shipping Information</h3>
	</div>
	<div class="section-body">		
		<fieldset class="clearfix">
			<div class="control-group">
				<button class="btn" type="button">Copy from Billing Information</button>
			</div>
			<div class="control-group complex">
				<label class="control-label">Name</label>
				<div class="row-fluid">
					<div class="span4">
						<div class="controls">
							<input type="text" class="input-text input-block-level">
							<span class="help-block">First</span>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="span8">
						<div class="controls">
							<input type="text" class="input-text input-block-level">
							<span class="help-block">Last</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="control-group complex">
				<label class="control-label">Shipping Address</label>
				<div class="controls">
					<input type="text" class="input-text input-block-level">
					<span class="help-block">Street Address</span>
				</div>
				<div class="row-fluid">
					<div class="span6">
						<div class="controls">
							<input type="text" class="input-text input-block-level">
							<span class="help-block">City</span>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="span6">
						<div class="controls">
							{% include "select-state" %}
							<span class="help-block">State</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="row-fluid">
					<div class="span6">
						<div class="controls">
							<input type="text" class="input-text input-block-level">
							<span class="help-block">Zip Code</span>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="span6">
						<div class="controls">
							{% include "select-country" %}
							<span class="help-block">Country</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="control-group">
				<label class="control-label">Notes</label>
				<div class="controls">
					<textarea class="textarea input-block-level" rows="5"></textarea>
					<span class="help-block">Notes about your order (e.g. special notes for delivery)</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</fieldset>
		<div class="message shipping-message">
			<h6>Customizable shipping message</h6>
			<p>Nullam id dolor id nibh ultricies vehicula ut id elit. Praesent commodo cursus magna, vel elerisque nisl consectetur et. Aenean eu leo quam. Pellentesque ornare sem lacinia quam enenatis vestibulum. Nullam quis risus eget urna mollis ornare vel eu leo.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>